381
00:31:38,375 --> 00:31:40,083
- It's a power-consumption thing.
- All right.

382
00:31:40,166 --> 00:31:43,000
And if there's a catastrophic failure
in a single module,

383
00:31:43,083 --> 00:31:45,291
