Watch your head.

384
00:31:46,041 --> 00:31:47,291
...you have to close this hatch.

385
00:31:47,375 --> 00:31:48,458
So bye-bye, David.

386
00:31:50,375 --> 00:31:52,541
This is the magnetic radiation-proofing.

387
00:31:53,041 --> 00:31:55,208
In case there's a solar storm,
come in here.

388
00:31:57,041 --> 00:31:58,916
I realize your first visit
was a little intense,

389
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:01,625
but this happens to be my favorite spot
